edicine&amp;rft.date=2005&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.isbn=9780226113692&amp;rft.place=Chicago&amp;rft.pub=University+of+Chicago+Press&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li>\n<li> <span class=\"citation book\">Collins, Harry M.; Evans, Robert (2007). <i>Rethinking expertise</i>. Chicago: University of Chicago Press. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780226113623\" title=\"Special:BookSources/9780226113623\">9780226113623</a>.</span><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHarry+Collins&amp;rft.au=Collins%2C+Harry+M.&amp;rft.au=Evans%2C+Robert&amp;rft.aufirst=Harry+M.&amp;rft.aulast=Collins&amp;rft.btitle=Rethinking+expertise&amp;rft.date=2007&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.isbn=9780226113623&amp;rft.place=Chicago&amp;rft.pub=University+of+Chicago+Press&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li>\n<li> <span class=\"citation book\">Collins, Harry M. (2010). <i>Tacit and explicit knowledge</i>. Chicago: University of Chicago Press. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780226113807\" title=\"Special:BookSources/9780226113807\">9780226113807</a>.</span><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHarry+Collins&amp;rft.au=Collins%2C+Harry+M.&amp;rft.aufirst=Harry+M.&amp;rft.aulast=Collins&amp;rft.btitle=Tacit+and+explicit+knowledge&amp;rft.date=2010&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.isbn=9780226113807&amp;rft.place=Chicago&amp;rft.pub=University+of+Chicago+Press&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li>\n<li> <span class=\"citation book\">Collins, Harry M. (2011). <i>Gravity's ghost: scientific discovery in the twenty-first century</i>. Chicago: The University of Chicago Press. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780226113562\" title=\"Special:BookSources/9780226113562\">9780226113562</a>.</span><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHarry+Collins&amp;rft.au=Collins%2C+Harry+M.&amp;rft.aufirst=Harry+M.&amp;rft.aulast=Collins&amp;rft.btitle=Gravity%27s+ghost%3A+scientific+discovery+in+the+twenty-first+century&amp;rft.date=2011&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.isbn=9780226113562&amp;rft.place=Chicago&amp;rft.pub=The+University+of+Chicago+Press&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li>\n<li> <span class=\"citation book\">Collins, Harry M.; <a href=\"/wiki/Trevor_Pinch\" title=\"Trevor Pinch\">Pinch, Trevor</a> (2014) [1998]. <i>The Golem at large: what you should know about technology</i> (6th ed.). Cambridge: Cambridge University Press. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/9781107688285\" title=\"Special:BookSources/9781107688285\">9781107688285</a>.</span><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHarry+Collins&amp;rft.au=Collins%2C+Harry+M.&amp;rft.aufirst=Harry+M.&amp;rft.aulast=Collins&amp;rft.au=Pinch%2C+Trevor&amp;rft.btitle=The+Golem+at+large%3A+what+you+should+know+about+technology&amp;rft.date=2014&amp;rft.edition=6th&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.isbn=9781107688285&amp;rft.place=Cambridge&amp;rft.pub=Cambridge+University+Press&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li>\n<li> <span class=\"citation book\">Collins, Harry M. (2014). <i>Are we all scientifi